```plantuml
@startuml SpektraSystems_CloudLabs-Azure

actor User

participant "On-premises Hyper-V" as HyperV
participant "Azure Migrate" as Migrate
participant "Azure Virtual Machines" as VMs
participant "Azure Functions" as Functions
participant "Azure Cosmos DB" as CosmosDB
participant "Azure Storage" as Storage
participant "Azure Monitor" as Monitor
participant "Azure Active Directory" as AAD
participant "Azure Log Analytics" as LogAnalytics
participant "Grafana" as Grafana

User -> Migrate: Initiate Azure Migrate project
Migrate -> HyperV: Assess on-premises VMs
HyperV -> Migrate: VMs assessment data

User -> Migrate: Start server replication
Migrate -> VMs: Deploy replicated VMs

User -> VMs: Connect to VMs
User -> VMs: Install IIS for web hosting

User -> Functions: Publish Azure Functions
Functions -> AAD: Add authentication

User -> Functions: Request data
Functions -> CosmosDB: Retrieve data

User -> Storage: Deploy Blazor website

User -> Monitor: Monitor Azure resources
Monitor -> LogAnalytics: Collect logs
LogAnalytics -> Grafana: Visualize metrics

@enduml
```